{"word":"G3973 - παύω - paúō - pow'-o - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pow'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முடி, நில், அமர், ஓய்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to make to cease or desist: to restrain refrain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primn. verb (&ldquo;pause&rdquo;); to <i>stop</i> (transitive or intransitive), that is, <i>restrain</i>, <i>quit</i>, <i>desist</i>, <i>come to an end:</i> - cease, leave, refrain."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}